                          Pendleton Resident Agency

                               116 South Main

                                   Suite 7

                           Pendleton, Oregon 97801

                                541-276-1433

   The Pendleton Resident Agency's territory includes the Oregon counties
   of Baker, Gilliam, Malheur, Morrow, Sherman, Umatilla, Union and
   Wallowa. This territory includes two Indian Reservations. It
   encompasses approximately 26,000 square miles, spanning approximately
   290 miles north to south and 215 miles east to west. The approximate
   population of this territory is 143,000.

